All Implemented Interfaces:
Codec
public class ZMBVCodec
extends AbstractVideoCodec

Implements the DosBox Capture Codec "ZMBV".

This codec currently only supports decoding from the file format into a BufferedImage. Encoding support may be added in the future.

For details seee ZMBVCodecCore.
